Pet.docs: A pet for sale in the pet store

__package__.yml.rawContents:
service:
  auth: false
  base-path: ''
  endpoints:
    listAllPets:
      path: /pets
      method: GET
      source:
        openapi: ../openapi.yml
      display-name: List all pets
      response:
        docs: A list of pets
        type: Pet
        status-code: 200
      examples:
        - response:
            body:
              id: 0
              category:
                id: 6
                name: name
              name: doggie
              photoUrls:
                - photoUrls
                - photoUrls
              tags:
                - id: 1
                  name: name
                - id: 1
                  name: name
              status: available
  source:
    openapi: ../openapi.yml
types:
  Error:
    properties:
      code: optional<integer>
      message: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Category:
    docs: A category for a pet
    properties:
      id: optional<long>
      name: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Tag:
    docs: A tag for a pet
    properties:
      id: optional<long>
      name: optional<string>
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  PetStatus:
    enum:
      - available
      - pending
      - sold
    docs: pet status in the store
    inline: true
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml
  Pet:
    docs: A pet for sale in the pet store
    properties:
      id: optional<long>
      category: optional<Category>
      name: string
      photoUrls: list<string>
      tags: optional<list<Tag>>
      status:
        type: optional<PetStatus>
        docs: pet status in the store
    source:
      openapi: ../openapi.yml

rootApiFile.rawContents:
name: api
error-discrimination:
  strategy: status-code
display-name: URL Reference API
